OL,3,CFamily of man killed then dismembered
OL,4,C'haunted' by his murder
OL,6,FStuart's brother Richard pays tribute
OL,7,Fto 'a truly unique and special human
OL,8,Fbeing'.
OL,10,FThe loved ones of Stuart Everett say
OL,11,Fthey are "haunted" by what happened to
OL,12,Fhim as his killer was jailed for his
OL,13,Fmurder and dismemberment.
OL,15,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, faces a life
OL,16,Fsentence after bludgeoning Stuart
OL,17,FEverett, 67, with a hammer, then using
OL,18,Fa hacksaw to cut him up into 27 pieces
OL,19,Fbefore dumping his body parts across
OL,20,FSalford and Manchester.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@RO]
