OL,6,FHe was convicted by a jury after just
OL,7,Fone hour and 36 minutes of
OL,8,Fdeliberations, following a three-week
OL,9,Ftrial at Manchester Crown Court.
OL,11,FOutside court, Richard Ziemacki, the
OL,12,Fvictim's older brother from the
OL,13,Ffamily's hometown of Derby, thanked
OL,14,Fpolice and the jury.
OL,16,FHe added: "Even though it's been
OL,17,Falmost 12 months we are still haunted
OL,18,Fby what happened. This has been made
OL,19,Feven more difficult knowing the
OL,20,Flengths that has gone into
OL,21,Forchestrating my brother's death.
OL,26,@xD@KOU
