OL,4,C'haunted' by his murder
OL,6,F"Benny is our family nickname for our
OL,7,Fendearing and loving Stuart.
OL,9,F"For any person to be treated in the
OL,10,Fway he was, brutally murdered, and
OL,11,Fsystematically and comprehensively
OL,12,Fdisposed of, has meant our family have
OL,13,Fbeen left traumatised beyond belief.
OL,15,F"Our family is now incomplete.
OL,17,F"The past 12 months have been some of
OL,18,Fthe most challenging our family has
OL,19,Fever had to endure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUwD@AOUyD@AOU
