OL,3,CFamily of man killed then dismembered
OL,4,C'haunted' by his murder
OL,6,F"But this has been made just that
OL,7,Flittle bit easier because of the
OL,8,Foutpouring of love and comforting
OL,9,Fwords from people across Greater
OL,10,FManchester, from Derby and beyond, who
OL,11,Fhave all come together to mourn with
OL,12,Fus a truly unique and special human
OL,13,Fbeing."
OL,15,FMr Ziemacki then read the inscription
OL,16,Fon his brother's funeral Urn.
