OL,6,FHe said: "Those we love don't go away,
OL,7,Fthey walk with us every day. Unseen,
OL,8,Funheard but always near. Still loved,
OL,9,Fstill missed and very dear. Justice
OL,10,Ffor Benny."
OL,12,FAlongside him, Detective Chief
OL,13,FSuperintendent Lewis Hughes, who led
OL,14,Fthe murder inquiry, said: "This is a
OL,15,Fcase of rarely seen complexity and
OL,16,Fscale, with detectives initially
OL,17,Fresponding to partial human remains
OL,18,Ffound deep within a secluded wood.
