OL,6,F"We started with nothing, but today we
OL,7,Fhave secured justice for Stuart
OL,8,FEverett, justice in the most
OL,9,Fchallenging of circumstances.
OL,11,F"We truly felt the public's support
OL,12,Fthroughout this investigation, the
OL,13,Fconcern and compassion shown has
OL,14,Fultimately helped us get to where we
OL,15,Fare today.
